snippet.title: Sporestory announcement trailer
snippet.description:
https://possiblyaxolotl.itch.io/sporestory
I'm not planning on making a devlog on this game as I see it as a way longer project I can work on in-between video projects. My plan is also to try and market this more as just a game developer and learn more about marketing video games besides making a hyper-edited ADHD enthralling devlog on my main channel
